title: 24 Sassy Cat Memes Being Seriously Silly Billys and Bringing Smiles to Your Feline-Loving Face
description: Hello cat pawrents, how are you doing this week? Whether you're doing great or a little less, you have one thing that makes any day better - a cat. Or two. Or five. Who counts, really? When it comes to cats math loses its meaning, 1 cat + 1 cat can sometimes be equal to 6 cats in total. It is known that cats constantly break the laws of physics, with them being liquid and all, but the laws of math also don't really apply to them. But that works best for us, cat pawrents, because even 1 cat can bring us the happiness that at least 10 cats bring. Or, like, at least 17 cats, we think. Cat math is complicated.So we bring you here a bunch of cat memes that hold the power to spread joy. Since there are 24 cat memes here, it means that it can bring happiness equivalent to about 1,743 cats, if not more.
author: Ayala Sorotsky
